literals.name: DefaultTraceStateDisabled
literals.description:
The default trace state is disabled
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1

literals.name: DefaultTraceStateEnabled

enumerations.name: LogTraceDefaultLogLevelEnum
enumerations.note: This enum defines available log&trace log levels that may be used to define the severity level of a log message. Aggregated by DltLogChannel.logTraceDefaultLogThreshold, DltLogSink.defaultLogThreshold

literals.name: error
literals.description:
Error with impact to correct functionality
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1

literals.name: info
literals.description:
High level information off logging is turned off
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=6

literals.name: warn
literals.description:
